title: 64. Young Voices of Seattle with Sarah Burk, Siyu Qu, and Will Crothers
description: This week, Vikram sits down with young professionals Sarah Burk, Siyu Qu and Will Crothers to talk about the scene, culture, aesthetic, and ethics of Seattle’s practicing architectural community in the city today.
